data.description:
Welcome home to this stunning 4 bed 2 bath dream home nestled in one of the best neighborhoods Watertown has to offer. Completely updated, enter from the driveway where you have a choice to make. Go straight through to the beautiful, private and fenced in patio out back with plenty of room to host a BBQ and cool off in the pool, go left into the attached garage, or go right into the cozy family room where you can enjoy a movie by the fire. Downstairs you'll also find 2 bedrooms, a full bath, and the laundry room. Going up the stairs, you'll find the open concept kitchen with quartz counter tops and stainless steel appliances, dining room and living room. Enjoy your morning coffee on the deck, or the warmth of another fire place in the living room. Upstairs you will also find 2 more bedrooms and a full bath. Updates completed as follows:
2020: Roof, siding, kitchen, appliances.
2021: pool filter. 
2022: Windows, floors
2023: deck outside dining room, concrete around pool, patio, mini splits
